name: Kinja Tee - Ocean
description:
What’s a “kinja” you ask?

kin·ja | \ ˈkin-jə , -(ˌ)jä\
noun, plural kinja also kinjas
Definition: A kindness ninja; a person trained in the martial art of kindness, employed especially for peace and the creation of positive solutions for the greater good.

 

Why you’ll love it

The kinja, or kindness ninja, is at the heart of our logo, and at the heart of everyone. We like to think kindness is in all of us just waiting for the right moment to pop up. So as you go about your day, passing on kindness, smile — you have a little kinja in you, too. We chose this tee made from organic cotton to reduce the water required to make our garments, and steer clear of pesticides and GMOs. Now that’s something to smile about.

 

Features

  • Unisex design for both women and men
  • 100% ring-spun organic cotton
  • Super soft hand feel
  • Made in the USA
